					<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171231163012/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Lk/ch_1">1</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171231163012/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Lk/ch_2">2</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171231163012/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Lk/ch_3">3</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171231163012/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Lk/ch_4">4</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171231163012/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Lk/ch_5">5</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171231163012/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Lk/ch_6">6</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171231163012/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Lk/ch_7">7</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171231163012/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Lk/ch_8">8</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171231163012/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Lk/ch_9">9</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171231163012/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Lk/ch_10">10</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171231163012/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Lk/ch_11">11</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171231163012/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Lk/ch_12" class="active">12</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171231163012/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Lk/ch_13">13</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171231163012/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Lk/ch_14">14</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171231163012/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Lk/ch_15">15</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171231163012/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Lk/ch_16">16</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171231163012/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Lk/ch_17">17</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171231163012/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Lk/ch_18">18</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171231163012/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/Lk/ch_19">19</a> <a 